document.title: NI 43-101 Technical Report for the Mount Milligan Project in North America dated October 2009.pdf
document.description: This report provides a comprehensive feasibility update for the Mt. Milligan copper-gold porphyry project located in Northern British Columbia, detailing geological, metallurgical, environmental, and financial analyses to support the project's development and economic viability.
